About

tvshowlist (http://tvshowlist.appspot.com/) is a simple online tool to track your personal collection of TV shows.  It hooks into the database at thetvdb.com to query show and episode information.

Components

Uses the nice tvdb_api python library (http://github.com/dbr/tvdb_api) along with a couple of minor modifications.  Hosted on Google App Engine (http://code.google.com/appengine/) using their python stack.

